Description:
SOLD BY NICK MAKROGLOU!
Stockdale Leggo Real Estate proudly present 10 Chiswick Crescent Derrimut. Professionally designed and meticulously inspected and looked after from the day building commenced to the present, the lucky purchaser can be assured of years of joyous living in a product far superior to other homes in the area. Upon entering you will be immediately impressed by the high ceilings and lovely Brushbox basketweave parquetry flooring and then blown away by the superb kitchen and gorgeous bathrooms. Downstairs consists of open plan kitchen/meals/ living area with adjacent alfresco, formal living and dining room, separate rumpus and study, laundry and powder room. Moving up the Tasmanian Oak hardwood staircase the second level offers 4 bedrooms serviced by 2 bathrooms with a large retreat area . Other features include granite benches (40mm to kitchen) and splashbacks in all wet areas, vinyl wrap upgrades to all cabinets throughout the home, quality fixtures and fittings, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, 3 KW solar panel system, high ceilings, high doors, ducted vacuum, feature walls, underground watering system, 24 hour continuous hot water, 2500 litre water tank plumbed to WCs, extra oversized remote garage (8x6m with 4-door storage and shelving units) with rear drive through and established gardens providing lovely views from all rooms and privacy from neighbours. All this on a very large block of approximately 682 sqm.

Description:
Ultimate entertainers delight in Brimbank Gardens
Experience designer living at its finest with this stunning two year young (approx) Porter Davis home. The front of the home presents all of the sleeping quarters including the main bedroom with en suite and walk in robe whilst the rear of the home is an entertainer's dream which includes a spacious study, kitchen with stainless steel appliances and walk in pantry, open plan living and dining area, rumpus/home theatre room and outdoor decked alfresco entertaining area. Inspect at the open for inspection this Saturday or contact the agent for a private inspection or more information.
- Featuring three bedrooms plus separate study/home office, the main bedroom appointed with walk in robe and lavish en suite complete with oversized shower. Bedrooms two and three are each fitted with double built in robes.
- Expansive modern kitchen with stainless steel cooking appliances including 900mm free standing cooker, range hood, dishwasher, stone topped island bench, walk in pantry and glass splash back.
- Elegant open plan living spaces that include the central dining and living area adjacent kitchen perfectly finished with timber floating floor boards plus separate rumpus/home theatre room.
- Sliding doors lead to the covered timber decked alfresco complete with ceiling fan and down lights perfect for year-round entertaining,
- 22 squares of living (approx) set on 448m2 block (approx).
- Complete with luxury features including remote control double garage with internal access, ducted heating, separate laundry, timber floating floor boards, down lights, front and rear landscaped gardens, and lots more!
Located just 17kms from Melbourne's CBD, Brimbank Gardens estate offers the benefits of excellent connectivity with bus services running through the community to nearby Deer Park and Sunshine train stations, and the $331 million Deer Park By-Pass, open spaces and landscaped surrounds, Balmoral Park which offers seven hectares of recreational space including two football ovals, playgrounds, walking paths and basketball court, Derrimut Primary School and St Lawrence's Catholic School, YMCA Derrimut Community Centre and easy access to shopping and entertainment including Derrimut Village and Brimbank Shopping Centre.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.

Description:
SOLD BARRY PLANT
Offering a modern lifestyle and an abundant flow of natural light, this home is ideal for those looking for a warm, open and inviting residence to occupy. Situated in this sought after
location, this home is conveniently close to schools, shops, public transport, childcare facilities and freeway access. Boasting formal lounge, spacious bedrooms with built in robes, 2 bathrooms, well appointed kitchen area with stainless steel appliances and ample storage options.
Bright and spacious meals and family areas offer a versatile space to enjoy when entertaining. Additional appointments include landscaped gardens, ducted heating, evaporative cooling and a double remote garage with drive through access and alfresco area. With the perfect blend of style, comfort and location, this is an opportunity not to be missed.

SOLD BY NICK MAKROGLOU!
